                "href": "/profile/Sanjyot-Agureddy"
            },
            "answer_text": "If you want to demand, well then you can demand 50LPA also, but the question comes down to are you worth the demand you make. Hike and switches totally depends on the value you bring to the company and your negotiation skills. I have see talented guys gettings 10\u201330% hike only and also seen average guys pulling off over 100\u2013150% hikes. It all depends how you portray your skills and negotiate your deal, there is no set way of doing this. But if play are confident in your skills and can convience your worth to the company I guess you can ask for anything between 4.5lpa to 5.5 lpa ",
